name: 2022 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited 4xe Rubicon
desc: The Rubicon 4xe includes an electronic disconnecting sway bar for improved wheel articulation. Standard conveniences closely mirror the Sahara 4xe and include the 8.4-inch Uconnect 4C infotainment system, automatic LED headlights, LED fog lights, ambient LED interior lighting, and automatic climate control.

name: 2022 Ram 1500 TRX
desc: If you’re looking to blend in, keep looking. With eight extra inches of overall width, massive 35-inch tires and a menacing stance, TRX is unlike anything else on the road.

name: Chevrolet Corvette Stingray
desc: In addition to the all-new IMSA GTLM Championship Edition, the 2022 Corvette Stingray lineup features three new exterior colors: Hypersonic Gray, Caffeine and Amplify Orange Tintcoat 1. A new low-profile rear spoiler and the Z51 design front splitter will be offered on non-Z51 models.

name: 2022 LEXUS LX FOUR WHEEL DRIVE SUV
desc: Key safety features include: Standard automated emergency braking with pedestrian-and-bicyclist detection. Standard lane-departure warning with lane-keeping assist. Standard adaptive cruise control.

name: 2022 Land Rover Defender
desc: Unlimited possibilities. Make more of your world, choose from four accessory packs. Designed with integrity, durable and equipped with 21st century technology. Distinctive Design. All-Terrain Capability. New Infotainment System.

name: 2022 Ford F-150 Raptor
desc: The 2022 Ford F-150 Raptor R takes F-150 Raptor performance to an entirely new level. It will likely feature a variation of the supercharged 5.2-liter V-8 that's in the Mustang Shelby GT500, with an output of 760 hp and 625 lb-ft of torque.

name: 2022 Toyota Sienna 7 Passenger XSE
desc: The 2022 Sienna offers many premium features across the model line (depending on model grade), such as kick-open and closed sliding side doors and rear gate, four-zone climate control system, heated second-row Super-Long Slide captain’s chairs with ottomans, power tilt and telescoping steering column with heated steering wheel, a digital rear-view mirror, 10-in. color head-up display and 12-speaker JBL® Premium Audio system.
